title: Steel Trap-2008
description:
Movie Description
If attending a blow-out bash on the top floor of a tall skyscraper, don&#039;t respond to any text messages inviting you to a "V.I.P." party on the 27th floor because, nine times out of ten, they&#039;re from a guy who has transformed the very building into a self-contained murder machine by setting up an elaborate network of traps. It&#039;s SAW meets DIE HARD as seven not-so-lucky invitees ignore the advice.
